00:21:32,323 --> 00:21:36,483
last night I was doing a bit
of research on the old Internet,

364
00:21:36,483 --> 00:21:37,843
Googling Bangkok,

365
00:21:37,843 --> 00:21:41,723
and I've found us a very,
very interesting

366
00:21:41,723 --> 00:21:43,043
back street venue.

367
00:21:44,283 --> 00:21:46,483
Remember, delete history, Patrick.

368
00:21:47,923 --> 00:21:49,243
No need for that.

369
00:21:49,243 --> 00:21:53,923
Because what I'd actually
found was pick-up paradise.

370
00:22:01,923 --> 00:22:03,723
What've we got here, Pad?

371
00:22:03,723 --> 00:22:05,683
D-Max nirvana.

372
00:22:05,683 --> 00:22:10,523
This is the Mecca for all
things pick-up.

373
00:22:10,523 --> 00:22:12,043
Oh!

374
00:22:12,043 --> 00:22:13,723
Fellow D-Maxer there.

375
00:22:13,723 --> 00:22:15,443
Look at these D-Max, lads.

