00:22:15,443 --> 00:22:17,083
Look at this!

377
00:22:17,083 --> 00:22:19,763
I think they've even got you covered
here, Paddy, with graphics.

378
00:22:19,763 --> 00:22:21,243
Look at that one.

379
00:22:21,243 --> 00:22:22,363
How many turbochargers?

380
00:22:22,363 --> 00:22:26,403
That one's got two massive
blowers on it.

381
00:22:26,403 --> 00:22:28,963
Look at this, it goes all the way
around here.

382
00:22:28,963 --> 00:22:31,243
It carries on going.
There's everything.

383
00:22:32,603 --> 00:22:35,723
I'll tell you what, this makes
me feel a bit wistful for my past,

384
00:22:35,723 --> 00:22:37,603
for the max power years.

385
00:22:37,603 --> 00:22:40,403
When I was younger, I couldn't leave
stuff alone.

386
00:22:40,403 --> 00:22:42,923
If I bought a car, I had to
add the bits -

387
00:22:42,923 --> 00:22:45,843
the fancy Hi-Fi, the rims,
the lowering kit.

388
00:22:45,843 --> 00:22:49,363
It's just... It's a... It's a rite
of passage, isn't it?

389
00:22:49,363 --> 00:22:51,883
You want to just add things.

390
00:22:51,883 --> 00:22:54,043
Got to say, Pad, when I saw
your pick-up,

391
00:22:54,043 --> 00:22:56,363
I thought, "That's a
bit much, that."

392
00:22:56,363 --> 00:22:59,283
However, I get it now. I get it.

