00:22:59,283 --> 00:23:02,003
Good Lord, I could waste days here.

394
00:23:04,803 --> 00:23:08,123
But the market was only the warm up.

395
00:23:08,123 --> 00:23:09,963
And just around the corner,

396
00:23:09,963 --> 00:23:14,763
we found some of Thailand's proper
max power petrolheads.

397
00:23:17,563 --> 00:23:19,043
Wowsers.

398
00:23:19,043 --> 00:23:21,923
Check out the metal here.

399
00:23:25,203 --> 00:23:27,003
Look at that Lotus.

400
00:23:27,003 --> 00:23:28,203
Wow!

401
00:23:32,083 --> 00:23:33,643
Look at these.

402
00:23:36,763 --> 00:23:40,483
That might be the fastest Jazz
I've ever seen in my life.

