00:23:40,483 --> 00:23:44,083
Turns out Bangkok isn't
just mad for mods, though.

404
00:23:44,083 --> 00:23:46,123
This is mega!

405
00:23:46,123 --> 00:23:49,243
They also love a bit of drifting.

406
00:23:51,923 --> 00:23:53,123
Oh!

407
00:23:53,123 --> 00:23:54,323
Yes!

408
00:23:54,323 --> 00:23:56,083
Look at this behind. Look at this.

409
00:24:01,243 --> 00:24:03,883
Now, this was what we'd come to see.

410
00:24:05,203 --> 00:24:08,803
Another corner of the world
completely mad for tuning

411
00:24:08,803 --> 00:24:10,523
and tyre smoke.

412
00:24:22,763 --> 00:24:24,083
Fantastic.

413
00:24:25,163 --> 00:24:28,163
To get the full Thai
drift experience, though...

414
00:24:28,163 --> 00:24:29,723
Come on, then, McGuinness.

415
00:24:29,723 --> 00:24:32,963
..we nominated our
D-Max correspondent

416
00:24:32,963 --> 00:24:35,203
to go along for the ride.

417
00:24:35,203 --> 00:24:36,963
He's going to love this.

418
00:24:36,963 --> 00:24:38,723
He's going to love this.

