00:24:38,723 --> 00:24:40,163
Here we go.

420
00:24:40,163 --> 00:24:41,643
I'm Christy.

421
00:24:41,643 --> 00:24:44,203
Hi, Christy.  Nice to meet you.
Nice to meet you.

