00:25:57,683 --> 00:26:00,163
CHEERING AND APPLAUSE

442
00:26:03,563 --> 00:26:04,803
Did you enjoy it?

443
00:26:07,443 --> 00:26:11,363
So, Pad, how did you enjoy your
first experience

444
00:26:11,363 --> 00:26:13,563
of the Zed drift scene?

445
00:26:13,563 --> 00:26:15,283
Well, schoolboy error,

446
00:26:15,283 --> 00:26:18,123
I had a Thai green curry
before I got in the car

447
00:26:18,123 --> 00:26:21,163
and I just felt extremely queasy.

448
00:26:21,163 --> 00:26:22,843
Everything was spinning, hot sweats.

449
00:26:22,843 --> 00:26:24,923
But I wasn't on my own...
No, you weren't, Pads.

450
00:26:24,923 --> 00:26:27,443
As the day went on, I was getting
rougher and rougher.

451
00:26:27,443 --> 00:26:28,843
Did you have the curry, as well?

452
00:26:28,843 --> 00:26:30,923
Oh, no, worse than that,
